<L>__{interior starks' room, ward, alpine grove, day}
<A>__{starks is shown to his room by nurse harding stern, senior and her henchman, damon a burly orderly who relishes his command, however diluted it may be. damon unceremoniously puts starks' uniform on the bed. he and nurse harding wait at the door for starks to change into it. damon looks at starks his eyes inadvertently conceding that starks is more threatening than the common senile he marshals; starks stares him back deliberately conceding that he's right. starks turns around only then looking stunned in the sterile, cotton white room, wondering where his life disappeared to.}
